    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你出现在一间牢房，头痛欲裂，而且……身体里不止有你？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156640/extras/4549b3b4374e8d3b89d3d44c6addcee2.poster.avif?t=1763386751\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156640/extras/4549b3b4374e8d3b89d3d44c6addcee2.webm?t=1763386751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156640/extras/4549b3b4374e8d3b89d3d44c6addcee2.mp4?t=1763386751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《裂脑》</strong>是一款<strong>非对称性合作解谜游戏</strong>，你将与朋友<strong>共同控制一个角色</strong>，只是各有各的能力与操作方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位玩家负责角色的行动，另一位则提供关键信息和引导。你们能否成功走出这个地方，取决于彼此之间的沟通与协作，你们需要越过障碍，避开陷阱，才能引导角色走出六边光圈的监狱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏必须线上进行，需要两位玩家对话交流。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >非对称性操作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两位玩家共同控制一个角色，一人负责行动，一人负责引导。你们必须积极沟通、紧密配合，才有可能逃出六边光圈的监狱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156640/extras/2912ad8b83c5d5c9e386ea9564adfb4b.poster.avif?t=1763386751\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156640/extras/2912ad8b83c5d5c9e386ea9564adfb4b.webm?t=1763386751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156640/extras/2912ad8b83c5d5c9e386ea9564adfb4b.mp4?t=1763386751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不只是一座监狱……</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们要想成功越狱，就必须动用大脑和技巧，置身真实而又多样的关卡，面对不同的机制、挑战与惊险刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156640/extras/2f3c6323f3a6004b848514b422f34a39.poster.avif?t=1763386751\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156640/extras/2f3c6323f3a6004b848514b422f34a39.webm?t=1763386751\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156640/extras/2f3c6323f3a6004b848514b422f34a39.mp4?t=1763386751\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >谜题有待解答</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们为什么成了这个样子？你们这辈子都要这样生活在一起吗？不要畏惧，勇敢面对自己灵魂的深处，才有可能得到真相。</p>",
